  "instructions": [
    "In a large Dutch oven, heat the olive oil over medium heat. Add the sliced onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the beef cubes and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the beef stock cubes, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add 2 cups of water to the pot and bring to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 30 minutes.",
    "While the beef is cooking, toast the bread slices until lightly browned.",
    "To serve, place a toasted bread slice in the bottom of a bowl, then top with a portion of the beef and sauce.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro, if desired.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
